options.name: Circle Top
options.restrictionFormula: if (width < 29.5){  error = "Doesnt meet the minimum width of 29.5 inches" } else if (width > 95.5){    error = "Over the maximum width of 95.5" } else if (height != (width/2)){   error = "Height must be equal to half the Width." }

options.name: Circle Top w/Extended Leg
options.restrictionFormula: if (width < 29.5){  error = "Doesnt meet the minimum width of 29.5 inches" } else if (width > 95.5 ){    error = "Over the maximum width of 95.5" } else if (height < 20.5){  error = "Doesnt meet the minimum height of 20.5 inches" } else if (height > 108 ){    error = "Over the maximum height of 108" } else if (((height / 12) * (width / 12)) > 40){   error = "Over max glass size of 40sqft." } else if (height < parseFloat(leg) + 1){   error = "The Leg value must be more than 1 inch less than the height." } else if (!leg == null && (parseFloat(leg) < 8)){   error = "The Leg value must be at least 8 inches." }

options.name: Octagon
